Classes
 NameDescription
TLoggerResolver
Subresolver that will inject proper logger defined by the configuration. In order to use this resolver make sure to register TLoggingConfiguration.

Rules:

* Base classes are checked as well so registering TObject with some logger will make all objects log to that logger (unles their logger injections are named).

* Named injections will be ignored by this resolver.
